        sur les t-shirts) — code conservé pour les réactiver plus tard.

      Pack Digital
      <div class="product-card reveal" data-product='{"id":1,"name":"Pack Digital — Adam ✕ 4 langues","price":4.99,"icon":"🎵"}'>
        <span class="product-badge new" data-i18n="shop.new">Nouveau</span>
        <div class="product-image">
          <div class="product-image-bg"></div>
          <div class="product-image-emoji">🎵</div>
